Splunk has been issued U.S. [[patent]] number 7,937,344 "Machine Data Web"<ref>[http://patft.uspto.gov/netacgi/nph-Parser?Sect1=PTO2&Sect2=HITOFF&p=1&u=%2Fnetahtml%2FPTO%2Fsearch-bool.html&r=4&f=G&l=50&co1=AND&d=PTXT&s1=Splunk&OS=Splunk&RS=Splunk 7,937,344 "Machine Data Web"]</ref> and U.S. [[patent]] number 8,112,425 "Time Series Search Engine".<ref>[http://patft.uspto.gov/netacgi/nph-Parser?Sect1=PTO2&Sect2=HITOFF&p=1&u=%2Fnetahtml%2FPTO%2Fsearch-bool.html&r=1&f=G&l=50&co1=AND&d=PTXT&s1=Splunk&OS=Splunk&RS=Splunk 8,112,425 "Time Series Search Engine"]</ref>

